parameters:
You cannot go back if you proceed from here. Will
you continue?

Look at this... It's amazing, isn't it? It seems
like I've completely awakened. With the power of
the demon...
No way... If you do that, then...

Magical girls... they're such weak beings, they're
not needed.

Yes, it's the best to have demons ruling and
dominating this world, isn't it?
What are you saying... Wake up...

Konoha, listen to the voice of the demon... It's
amazing, you know... Hehe.

It seems like it's no use anymore... Baretta... I
will defeat you this time, for sure.

Ahahaha! If you think you can do it... then go
ahead and try!
For Freya's sake...! Baretta, I will save you!

......Uchiha...... I should be strong...... but...
ahhhhh...... my body...... is burningggggg

I somehow managed to fulfill Freya's wish... Well,
maybe I can't exactly say I fulfilled it.

At least, it's better than the way things are
now...

\C[3]You're the same... Konoha... Do you seek
power... If destruction, slaughter, cannot be
restrained...
Shut up...! I am who I am...
Guah...! Ugh... What kind of power is this...

As I thought, that's how it turned out, Konoha...
It's a shame...

But it's okay, if it's Lord Devil... I'm sure he
will guide you.

Losers don't have the right to choose, right? Now,
let's destroy this world together.
I will transform it into a world of demons...!

\C[14]I entered the Evil Route\C[3] and resigned
from the Magical Girl Guild.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Oh...? A magical girl
coming this far alone...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Without even breaking
through the Gate of Ten Thousand Demons, you've
entered the Flame Zone...? This is quite...
perplexing...

So there's a person called Devil here, let me
through.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] is saying interesting
things... However, their strength seems to be
genuine.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] I feel a conviction
in their proven strength... This is another
terrifying reincarnation of a magical girl.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0], but I can't let you
pass so easily... Let me show you what true
despair looks like...!

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0]... Ah... This much...
Is it...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Could it be... a true
magical girl...? Is that what you are...?
I'm not some true magical girl, I am me.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Hehe... I see... Well
then... Go ahead... I have lost...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] It would be good for
you to meet Lord Devil... You have the right to...
Defeat Devil and bring everything to an end...

Zetsuou Beruzevia, it's a shame. So, this is the
extent of it...

\c[10]I thought it might be Zetsuou
Beruzevia\c[0]... but it seems I was mistaken.

Zetsuou Beruzevia: Now, in the midst of despair,
continue to give birth to our children... Kukuku.
Hii... I hate this...! Ahhhhh! Ahhhhhh!

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Now, there will be no
mercy this time.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] I am the last
fortress protecting Lord Devil. If you cannot
surpass me, then you cannot lay eyes on Lord
Devil.

I understand. I will defeat you and go to Lord
Devil, that's all.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Beautiful... It's not
just a bluff...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0], it's not that I have
resigned myself to death, but rather, I have a
face that believes in myself.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Very well. Allow me
to show you the true meaning of despair...!

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] So... you truly are a
magical girl...
I'm not just any ordinary magical girl, I am me.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Hehe... I see... Well
then... Go ahead... I have lost...
Let's put an end to everything...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] I'm disappointed. So,
this is the extent of it...

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] I thought...
perhaps... but it seems I was mistaken.

\c[10]Zetsuou Beruzevia\c[0] Now, in the midst of
despair, continue to give birth to our children
forever... Kukuku.

Belzevia, the Supreme King\C[0] Fuhahahaha!
Excellent, Baretta. Hatred is the essence of
power. It seems you understand it well.

Konoha, you came. Yes, this person killed Frya. I
happened to witness it and chased after them.

Did you chase after \C[10]Supreme King
Belzevia\C[0]? What are you saying? I specially
invited you here. I must turn you back into a
Devil Witch again, you know.
Konoha, you'll help me, right? This one is tough.

Belzevia, the Supreme King... Fufu, how clever of
you. Well, it's fine. I can create clones, so I'll
take care of each of you personally.

This person... Seriously, they're messing
around...! Konoha, let's go!

\C[10]Supreme King Belzevia\C[0] No way... me...
guh... ohhh...

\C[10]Supreme King Belzevia\C[0], Devil-sama...
Please... lend me your power... Devil-sama...!

Phew... Looks like we managed to defeat them.
Thank you, Konoha. We wouldn't have been able to
do it without you.

So, the Devil you mentioned earlier... is the boss
of the demons? They're waiting ahead, huh?
I'm sure that's the case. What about Baretta?

Yeah, it's fine to continue like this, but I want
to report to Frya once. There's also the matter of
the corpses.

Alright, I understand. I'll leave it to Frya. I'll
go and see the Devil myself.

The enemy is surely formidable... Are you okay by
yourself?

I'm not exactly sure, but for some reason, I feel
like I know that Devil

I see... You must have been special since the time
of reincarnation, destined to be the key to this
battle. I'll leave the rest to you from here on.

Yes, leave it to me... I will definitely change
the prophecy of destruction.
Ahh...! What kind of... strength is this...

\C[10]The Demon King Belzevia\C[0] was still a
fleeting existence, a magical girl...

\C[10]The Demon King Belzevia\C[0], Baretta, has
undergone reeducation, while Konoha, who has shed
the flames of admonition... It's not necessary. In
fact, it would only cause trouble later on.

Belzevia, the Supreme King, to the eternal
prison...

Welcome, \c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0]. You've
done well to make it this far.

As I said before, \c[10]Supreme King
Belzevia\c[0], Konoha-san will not show any mercy
when we meet again. This is where it ends for you.

We've come this far, I won't let you go...
Baretta... Your appearance...

That's right, this is the true form of the Devil
Witch... Isn't it lovely? The greatest power is
overflowing...

Baretta, I will definitely save you... I will
definitely grant Frya's wish...!

Don't worry, I have already been saved... thanks
to Lord Devil... you know.

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0], can you
withstand our combined attack? Hehehe... Now,
Konoha... come at me!

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0] I am the Supreme
King Belzevia, who oversees the Four Heavenly
Kings... So you are the magical girl called
Konoha. I see, you truly live up to your title as
the savior...

So you're the one who instigated Baretta and
brought her here.

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0] No, it's not like
that. She is the embodiment of her own will. It
seems that the power of a weak magical girl is not
needed.

Konoha, you lost, so hurry up and join the demons.
Do you really think you can win in this state?

It's only natural. That's why I've come this far,
Baretta. I will definitely save you...

Don't worry, I have already been saved... thanks
to Lord Devil... you know.

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0], can you
withstand our combined attack? Hehehe... Now,
Konoha... come at me!

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0]... What...
incredible... power... to have come this far...

...Ah... My body... is... falling apart... I don't
want this... Please... help me... Lord Belzevia...

Did you let your guard down? It seems like you
don't have the same vigor as before.

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0]... Hehe...
Whether you defeat me or not... in the end... Lord
Devil will be there... In the depths of despair,
you will meet your final moments... Konoha...

Freya... I saved Baretta... though I can't say it
was for the best...

If we go further down to the lowest level...
everything will come to an end, won't it...
Ahh...! What kind of... strength is this...

\c[10]Supreme King Belzevia\c[0], you were still
such a fleeting existence, magical girl...
Konoha, weak individuals like you are unnecessary.

Konoha! Fryer was... killed by a demon I've never

Well then... Baretta, in order to protect Fryer...

I chased after them all the way here, but
unfortunately, I don't have the courage to go any
further from here...
Don't worry, I'll go from here.

I'm not sure what will happen, but I'm sure
everything will be resolved here. Baretta, you
should go back. It's dangerous.

I understand. I'll probably just be a burden at
home... I'll leave the rest to you.
